profile_positions.description:
1. Dataset sanity checks automation, preprocessing automation within AWS environment, using spark transformations;
2. Risk modeling for H2O legacy models and python models (ensembles: GLM+GBM): feature selection, feature tuning, hyperparameters tuning; 
3. Model evaluation and review: univariate and cross-variate analysis, cross validation, storing experiments with MLflow; 
4. Automation and scaling the whole process through Databricks workflows;
5. Close interactions with different domain teams.
Achievements: automated orchestrated ML pipeline drastically decreased amount of time needed for refitting tariff model. Incorporated feature tuning, feature selection and HPO improved quality of models.
